Package com.google.gwt.dev.shell.rewrite

Interface Summary
HostedModeClassRewriter.InstanceMethodOracle Maps instance methods to the class in which they are declared.
HostedModeClassRewriter.SingleJsoImplData Contains data about how SingleJsoImpl methods are to be dispatched.
 

Class Summary
HasAnnotation A simple ClassAdapter that determines if a specific annotation is declared on a type (ignoring any annotatons that may be present on supertypes or superinterfaces).
HostedModeClassRewriter This class performs any and all byte code rewriting needed to make hosted mode work.
RewriteJsniMethods Turns native method declarations into normal Java functions which perform the corresponding JSNI dispatch.
RewriteSingleJsoImplDispatches Effects the renaming of @SingleJsoImpl methods from their original name to their mangled name.
UseMirroredClasses A general Class Visitor which will take any of the method calls in it's list and replace them with static calls to another method (the "mirrored" method) in another class (the "mirrored" class).
